    <id>tag:developer.github.com,2020-10-01:/changes/2020-10-01-graduate-antiope-preview/</id>
    <title type="html">Antiope preview graduation</title>
    <published>2020-10-01T07:00:00Z</published>
    <updated>2020-10-01T07:00:00Z</updated>
    <link rel="alternate" href="https://developer.github.com/changes/2020-10-01-graduate-antiope-preview/"/>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;antiope&lt;/code&gt; preview is now an official part of the API. These preview headers are no longer required. The Checks API endpoints no longer require the &lt;code&gt;antiope&lt;/code&gt; preview header.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;application/vnd.github.antiope-preview+json
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For more information, see the "&lt;a href="https://docs.github.com/en/rest/reference/checks"&gt;Checks API&lt;/a&gt;."&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks again to everyone that tried out these API features during the preview period.&lt;/p&gt;</content>
